<br>
Vallon Zek: No &quot;single teaming&quot;, instead you get the lights ( humans, elves, shorts) VS the darks (dark elves, trolls, ogres).<br>
<br>
&quot;Light&quot; is the most powerful side on Vallon Zek.<br>
<br>
Tallon Zek: Bluebie clusterfuck with an ounce of PvP. Basically the whole server is 4-teaming, only a few &quot;light&quot; and &quot;dark&quot; guild remains.<br>
<br>
Sullon Zek: Good VS Neutral VS Evil.<br>
<br>
Good: Challenging (and I do mean it! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :b --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":b"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
Neutral: ... (does anyone still play neutral ? ;p)<br>
Evil: Too easy, more than half of the server is evil.<br>
<br>
<br>
Now, PvP as a mage is:<br>
<br>
FuX0rEd !!~<br>
<br>
1) Everyone and their mother got godly resists on PvP servers, especially since they're all pretty &quot;old&quot; now, Sullon Zek being the youngest.<br>
<br>
2) Unbalanced. Mages suck in PvP, pets are nerfed (only do half the dmg in VS PC's) and get rooted easily at lower levels. At higher level (45+) they usually can't do a dent in your foe's HP's, save epic pet VS casters.<br>
<br>
<br>
Best class for PvP: tankish .. rogues/monks/shadowknights/bards <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=fantik>Fantik </A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Mage</span><br>  Posts: 17<br> <font color=#333333>(5/6/02 4:15:02 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=83.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   PVP Question</span><hr size=1> Thank you very much. You gave me the exact information what I was looking for. Hmm. I love mages but it seems like a waste of time to make one on a pvp server. Not sure what I'm gonna do now. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=pepshikola>Pepshikola</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#333333>(7/4/02 7:21:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm27.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=83.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: PVP Question</span><hr size=1> Rallos Zek is the most cut-throat. People are always fighting there, especially in these zones:<br>
EC<br>
Oasis<br>
High Hold<br>
Any Newbie Zone<br>
Gfay<br>
Umm...<br>
There's lots more, I've played on the team pvp servers, and I didn't really see the point, all you have to lose is coin. On Rallos, most pk'ers have no drop gear or no gear. Heh, Mages are weak when it comes to pvp, because when you get raped by a pair of wizards, which you WILL if you play on rallos, they just root your pet, and nuke you. Mage PKing goes pretty much like this:<br>
Wizards, and other casters: Root pet, Nuke you<br>
Warriors, and other melee: Kill you, ignore pet<br>
<br>
